                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "For each fetched item, dynamic SQL statements are constructed to grant SELECT, INSERT, and UPDATE permissions to the specified domain user."
